    "attributes": {
        "action": "Give Universal Credit claimants the option to receive fortnightly payments",
        "additional_details": "Making one monthly payment last can be a struggle. Many families are struggling since being moved to Universal Credit. We believe this would be a particular help during the cost of living crisis, especially to claimants with children.",
        "background": "I would like the Government to give Universal Credit claimants the option to receive payments fortnightly, rather than monthly.",
